sourcesContent: import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';import { Provider } from 'react-redux';import React from 'react';import { store, history} from './store'; import { Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom';import { ConnectedRouter } from 'react-router-redux'; import App from './components/App'; ReactDOM.render(( <Provider store={store}> <ConnectedRouter history={history}> <Switch> <Route path="/" component={App} /> </Switch> </ConnectedRouter> </Provider> ), document.getElementById('root'));
